OL,3,CMan arrested 22 years after
OL,4,Cbusinessman's robbery murder
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof murder more than two decades after
OL,8,Fa businessman was killed during a
OL,9,Frobbery at his million-pound mansion.
OL,11,FJohn Luper, 57, died after an attack
OL,12,Fby masked intruders at his home on
OL,13,FSandmoor Drive in Leeds in February
OL,14,F2004.
OL,16,FWest Yorkshire Police said a man was
OL,17,Farrested in Bradford on Wednesday.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
