CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775923881
OL,3,CMan arrested 22 years after
OL,4,Cbusinessman's robbery murder
OL,6,FDet Supt Damian Roebuck said: "Our
OL,7,Finvestigation team are firmly
OL,8,Fcommitted to doing everything we can
OL,9,Fto get justice for John Luper and his
OL,10,Ffamily.
OL,12,F"This includes the analysis of
OL,13,Fforensic materials, which I can
OL,14,Fconfirm has led to today's arrest
OL,16,F"Mr Luper's family have been updated
OL,17,Fand, while we appreciate that the
OL,18,Farrest will understandably bring a
OL,19,Frenewed focus on the investigation, we
OL,20,Fdo not anticipate any immediate
OL,21,Fdevelopments at this stage.
OL,26,@nD@_OUxD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
