CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775923881
OL,3,CMan arrested 22 years after
OL,4,Cbusinessman's robbery murder
OL,6,F"It is more than 22 years since John's
OL,7,Fbrutal murder and we are no less
OL,8,Fdetermined to find out who killed him."
OL,10,FMr Luper was walking his dog near his
OL,11,Fhome when he was attacked on 16
OL,12,FFebruary 2004.
OL,14,FHe was dragged back to the property,
OL,15,Fwhere his wife, daughter and au pair
OL,16,Fwere tied up. The robbers escaped with
OL,17,Fabout #100,000 in valuables, including
OL,18,Fa rare Cartier watch
OL,20,FMr Luper was found unconscious and
OL,21,Fdied at the scene from asphyxiation.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
