PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775923881
OL,3,CMan arrested 22 years after
OL,4,Cbusinessman's robbery murder
OL,6,FDespite numerous appeals by police and
OL,7,Ffamily and a number of arrests during
OL,8,Fthe early stages of the investigation,
OL,9,Fno-one has been charged.
OL,11,FDet Supt Roebuck urged anyone who knew
OL,12,Fof people making inquiries into Mr
OL,13,FLuper and his business dealings around
OL,14,Fthe time of the murder to come forward
OL,16,FHe added: "Likewise, perhaps you were
OL,17,Fapproached and asked to buy jewellery
OL,18,Ffrom unknown people around the time of
OL,19,Fthe murder. This information could
OL,20,Fprove vital to our investigation."
OL,26,@xD@KOU|D@bO]
